    <header class="mb-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="bg-primary/20 text-primary font-label font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest px-3 py-1 rounded-full">{post.category}</span>
        <time class="font-body text-sm text-secondary">{post.date}</time>
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-headline text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter text-on-surface mb-4">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="font-body text-lg text="secondary leading-relaxed">{post.description}</p>
    </header>

    <section class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed space-y-6">
      <p>Malaysia's night market (pasar malam) and bazaar culture is a thriving, year-round ecosystem. From Ramadan bazaars in Selangor to weekly pasar malams in Cheras, Kajang, and Shah Alam, there are thousands of small vendors who need a steady supply of packaging materials — and most of them are not buying wholesale. This gap is exactly the opportunity a smart packaging reseller can fill.</p>

      <p>Quinocycle Sdn. Bhd. in Balakong, Selangor has supplied packaging resellers since 2010. In this guide, we explore how to build a profitable packaging reselling business targeting night market and bazaar vendors in the Klang Valley.</p>

      <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mt-10 mb-4">Understanding the Night Market Vendor's Packaging Problem</h2>
      <p>Most pasar malam and bazaar vendors are sole traders or micro-businesses. They are busy running their stalls 5–6 nights a week and have limited time or inclination to research wholesale suppliers. Their default behaviour is to buy packaging from the nearest convenience store, sundry shop, or Carrefour — paying retail prices for materials that wholesale buyers get at 40–60% less.</p>

      <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-semibold text-on-surface mt-6 mb-3">The Demand is Real and Consistent</h3>
      <p>Night market vendors have predictable, recurring packaging needs. A craft vendor needs small boxes for gifting. A food trader needs packaging bags or containers. A clothing stall needs poly bags. A toy or hobby seller needs bubble wrap for fragile items. The key insight is that once vendors find a reliable, affordable supplier, they become consistent repeat customers — often for years.</p>

      <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mt-10 mb-4">How to Build Your Night Market Packaging Reseller Business</h2>

      <div class="bg-surface-variant/50 border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-2xl p-6 my-8">
        <h3 class="font-headline text-lg font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Step-by-Step Reseller Launch Plan</h3>
        <div class="space-y-3 font-body text-sm">
          <div class="flex gap-4 py-2 border-b border-outline-variant/20">
            <span class="font-bold text-primary min-w-[24px]">1.</span>
            <span class="text-on-surface">Survey 2–3 local night markets. Count vendor types and estimate packaging needs per stall per week</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 py-2 border-b border-outline-variant/20">
            <span class="font-bold text-primary min-w-[24px]">2.</span>
            <span class="text-on-surface">Identify your top 5 SKUs (e.g. small boxes, bubble wrap, OPP tape, paper bags, poly bags)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 py-2 border-b border-outline-variant/20">
            <span class="font-bold text-primary min-w-[24px]">3.</span>
            <span class="text-on-surface">Buy your first batch wholesale from Quinocycle (min. RM 1,000) — focus on fast-moving items only</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 py-2 border-b border-outline-variant/20">
            <span class="font-bold text-primary min-w-[24px]">4.</span>
            <span class="text-on-surface">Approach vendors at the market with samples and pricing — offer weekly delivery or collection</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 py-2 border-b border-outline-variant/20">
            <span class="font-bold text-primary min-w-[24px]">5.</span>
            <span class="text-on-surface">Build a WhatsApp group for your vendors — take orders weekly, deliver before market days</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 py-2">
            <span class="font-bold text-primary min-w-[24px]">6.</span>
            <span class="text-on-surface">Reinvest margins into stock diversity — add more sizes and materials as customer base grows</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mt-10 mb-4">Targeting Ramadan Bazaar Season in Selangor</h2>
      <p>Ramadan bazaar season is the highest-volume period for Malaysian night market suppliers. Thousands of new food and merchandise stalls appear across Selangor each year during this month. Vendors preparing for Ramadan bazaars are actively looking for packaging suppliers in the weeks prior. If you can establish relationships with bazaar operators and stall aggregators before Ramadan starts, you can lock in significant pre-season orders.</p>

      <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-semibold text-on-surface mt-6 mb-3">Targeting Bazaar Organisers Directly</h3>
      <p>Many large bazaars are managed by event companies or community organisations that coordinate dozens or hundreds of stalls. Approaching these organisers — rather than individual vendors — with a proposal to be the recommended packaging supplier for all stalls can secure very large, consistent orders. Offer a small discount or free delivery above a minimum combined order threshold to make the value proposition compelling.</p>

      <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mt-10 mb-4">Margin and Pricing Strategy</h2>
      <p>Buy wholesale from Quinocycle at RM 1.90–6.50 per box depending on size. Add your margin and sell to vendors at RM 3.00–10.00 per box — typically at or slightly below what vendors currently pay at retail. You stay below the vendor's current cost, so they have clear motivation to switch. Your margin is the difference, and volumes compound as your customer base grows.</p>

      <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mt-10 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 my-6">
        {faqSchema.mainEntity.map((faq) => (
          <details class="bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 rounded-xl p-4">
            <summary class="font-label font-semibold text-on-surface cursor-pointer">{faq.name}</summary>
            <p class="font-body text-secondary mt-3 leading-relaxed">{faq.acceptedAnswer.text}</p>
          </details>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 rounded-2xl p-8 my-10 text-center">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-3">Start Your Packaging Reseller Business with Quinocycle</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-secondary mb-6">Quinocycle in Balakong, Selangor is the wholesale supplier behind many successful packaging resellers in the Klang Valley. Min. order RM 1,000. Competitive pricing, reliable stock.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href={WA_LINK} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-primary text-on-primary font-label font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-full hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
            WhatsApp to Become a Reseller
          </a>
          <a href="mailto:quinocycle@gmail.com" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 border border-primary text-primary font-label font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-primary/5 transition-colors">
            Email: quinocycle@gmail.com
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-xs text-secondary mt-4">No.13, Jalan Taming P/1, Taming Jaya, Balakong, Selangor 43300 · Mon–Fri 9am–6pm, Sat 9am–1pm</p>
      </div>

      <p>The night market and bazaar vendor community represents one of the most accessible and rewarding reseller markets in Malaysia. High demand, recurring orders, and low price sensitivity around value make it ideal for a new or growing packaging reseller. Start your supply relationship with Quinocycle today — and start building your own customer base from there.</p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>
